Nov 27 16:32:06 manet kernel: FS:  0000000000000000(0000) GS:ffff88846fa40000(0000) knlGS:0000000000000000
Nov 27 16:32:06 manet kernel: CS:  0010 DS: 0000 ES: 0000 CR0: 0000000080050033
